Token.Abstract: The AdInterstitialViewDelegate protocol defines methods that a delegate of a AdInterstitialView object can optionally implement to receive notifications from ad.
Sent after an ad interstitial view closed and tracks the usage time of ad interstitial view.

Parameter.Name: sender
Parameter.Abstract: The ad interstitial view was closed.

Parameter.Name: usageTimeInterval
Parameter.Abstract: The usage time interval of ad interstitial view.
